Howdy, everybody! As I prep for the Islaverse plot, I wanted to go ahead and drop some ~spoilies~ in your lap before we go live. More specifically, I wanted to share with you the planned universes and groups for the plot so that you can have the opportunity to preplan some fun and possible drama along the way. Additionally, if you have any ideas or wants from the upcoming plot that I can offer, just let me know and I'll (try!) to fit it in.<br><br>

